Package: NIRApost
Title: Post-Hoc Analysis Tools for NodeIdentifyR Algorithm (NIRA) in Psychological Networks
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Fei", "Wang", 
           email = "bjnwangfei0501@outlook.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8283-1363"))
Description: 
    Provides comprehensive post-hoc analytical methods for nodeIdentifyR algorithm (NIRA)
    in psychological research. Key features include:
    - Dichotomous Data Imputation with Multiple Methods
    - Permutation testing for intervention effects
    - Network stability evaluation based on repeated simulation
    - Moderated network analysis
    - Advanced visualization of symptom network dynamics
